// INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P908238651" "When is Longbow going to get here? I REALLY don't want to be guarding this guy...<em t=5>Yeah...you think even {HeroName} would show up?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3378617958" "It's {HeroName}...!!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1269743023" "Tell me something I don't know. It's tough enough being a cop in the Isles. <em t=2> But then guarding a guy who EVERYONE would be after if they found out about his secret?! <em t=5>I wouldn't put it past {Hero.gender=male him|her}, that's for sure."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3922484802" "I knew this could only end badly!"

